headline: How Much Upside is Left in Universal Health Services (UHS)? Wall Street Analysts Think 28.75%
summary: The average of price targets set by Wall Street analysts indicates a potential upside of 28.8% in Universal Health Services (UHS). While the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric is questionable, the positive trend in earnings estimate revisions might translate into an upside in the stock.
